{
  "_pack": "legal",
  "_about": "Starter pack for legal-AI startups. CONSERVATIVE by design: clause extraction, redlines, and contract summaries route Opus->Sonnet (never Haiku), and a profile floor of Sonnet prevents anything cheaper. Long-form drafting (briefs/petitions) is left to the global router (stays on the strong model). Load with MODELPILOT_POLICY=packs/legal.json.",
